; Level 2: Button + Door teaching level.
; Puzzle: player and box start at grid (2,2) = world (4,4).
; Button at grid (3,1)=world(6,2), door at grid(3,2)=world(6,4).
; Goal at grid (4,2)=world(8,4) — in row 2, behind the door.
; The box still needs to be routed onto the button before the player can cross the door.

